Package: StatML
Title: Interactive Machine Learning Platform for Ecology and Data Science
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Manuel", "Spínola", , "manuel.spinola@una.cr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application for machine learning, part of the 
    StatSuite ecosystem. Covers regression and classification using linear models, 
    generalized linear models, and random forests with tidymodels. Designed for 
    teaching and research in ecology, biodiversity sciences, and data science.
